<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
    <meta name="renderer" content="webkit">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <%- include("../include/public") %>

    <style type="text/css">
        * {
            list-style-type: none;
        }

        /*导航*/
        #help {
            background-color: #000000;
            position: relative;
        }

        #help .navbar-default .navbar-nav > li > a {
            color: #FFF;
        }

        /*底部样式*/
        .footer_help {
            margin-top: 25px;
            background-color: #373737;
            width: 100%;
            height: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 50px;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }

        /*页面内容样式*/
        h3 {
            padding-left: 198px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #FFFFFF;">
<%- include("../include/header") %>
<!-- 页面内容 -->
<div class="container" style="padding: 20px 0;">
    <div class="row" style="box-shadow: 0 5px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.13);padding: 65px 0;">
        <div class="col-sm-7" style="border-right: 1px solid #e5e4e4;">
            <div style="width: 60%;margin: auto;">
                <h3>登&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;录</h3>
                <form class="form-horizontal" id="loginForm">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="" class="col-sm-3 control-label">用户名</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-9">
                            <input name="userName" class="form-control"  placeholder="请输入用户名">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="" class="col-sm-3 control-label">密码</label>
                        <div class="col-sm-9">
                            <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control"  placeholder="请输入密码">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <div style="float: right;padding-right: 16px;margin-top: -9px;">
                            <a href="/public/page/forgetPassword">忘记密码?</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <div class="col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-9">
                            <button type="button" id="loginBtn" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 6px 131px;">登录
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-5" style="padding: 21px 50px;">
            <p>还不是安宝用户？<a href="/public/page/register">立即注册</a></p>
            <p>您还可以关注安宝微信，随时掌控最新资讯！</p>
            <p><img src="/images/img/ab_gzh.png"/></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<%- include("../include/buttom") %>
<script src="/javascripts/utils/popupUtils.js"></script>
<script src="/javascripts/function/login.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
